title: Garmin Bluechart G2 Vision VEU504S - Black and Caspian Sea
description:
The new Garmin G2 charts don't go into MapSource only to Garmin Mobile PC, but to use the full potential (e.g. embedded photographic images) you have to use it on a GPS that supports G2 Vision BlueCharts.
BlueChart G2 Vision maps are only sold on SD cards!!!

Detailed coverage of the Caspian Sea in its entirety and the Volga River from Novocheboksarsk to Volzhskiy. Includes Chistopol' and Samara. General coverage of the North Aegean Sea.
